A game by Middlerun
http://www.middlerun.net

A 2D Minecraft-style game.

Controls:
Movement:      WASD
Break block:   Left mouse
Place block:   Right mouse
Select block:  Scroll wheel
Jump:          Space


Requires LÖVE 0.7.2. See http://www.love2d.org for more info.


